## What`s dmr-source

Dmr-source is source modules of dmr framework.
The source is the abstraction of the DMR framework input.
dmr-source will support different kinds of storage such as local file / remote (http / ftp) / hadoop / ssh2...

- [x] Source
- [x] FileSource
- [x] HttpSource
- [x] FtpSource
- [ ] SftpSource
- [ ] HadoopSource

